high_descs: Turn right and walk across the kitchen to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn to the right and step right to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Turn left and step left to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the knife on the edge of the counter.
Turn to the right and step right to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Turn around and walk across to face the microwave on the counter.
Heat the apple piece and remove it from the microwave.
Turn to the right to face the counter.
Place the piece of apple on the counter next to the stove.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it on the counter by the toaster.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the counter with the fork, turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the counter to the right of the stove.
Cut the apple on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge then turn right and walk to the counter with the toaster on it.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn right and walk to towards the stove.
Pick up an apple slice from the counter to the right of the stove.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave and take the apple out.
Turn right and face the counter with the toaster on it.
Put the apple slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked apple slice on the counter.
